{"title":"Java各种时间日期相关操作","date":"2021-01-14T14:29:51.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 14, 2021","L":"01/14/2021","MM-DD":"01-14"},"link":"2021/01/14/Java各种时间日期相关操作","tags":["日期"],"updated":"2021-01-14T14:49:19.530Z","content":"<h3 id=\"获取两个日期之间的所有日期\">获取两个日期之间的所有日期<a title=\"#获取两个日期之间的所有日期\" href=\"#获取两个日期之间的所有日期\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> List&lt;String&gt; <span class=\"title\">getBetweenDays</span><span class=\"params\">(String start, String end)</span> <span class=\"keyword\">throws</span> ParseException </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tList&lt;String&gt; date = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tSimpleDateFormat simpleDateFormat = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> SimpleDateFormat(<span class=\"string\">&quot;yyyy-MM-dd&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tDate startTime = simpleDateFormat.parse(start);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tDate endTime = simpleDateFormat.parse(end);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tCalendar startDate = Calendar.getInstance();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tstartDate.setTime(startTime);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tstartDate.add(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR, <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tCalendar endDate = Calendar.getInstance();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tendDate.setTime(endTime);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tdate.add(simpleDateFormat.format(startTime));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (startDate.before(endDate)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tdate.add(simpleDateFormat.format(startDate.getTime()));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tstartDate.add(Calendar.DAY_OF_YEAR, <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tdate.add(simpleDateFormat.format(endTime));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> date;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","next":{"title":"Hello World","link":"2021/01/10/hello-world"},"plink":"http://example.com/2021/01/14/Java各种时间日期相关操作/","toc":[{"id":"获取两个日期之间的所有日期","title":"获取两个日期之间的所有日期","index":"1"}]}